      <p><strong>How this review was built:</strong> We did not purchase, install, or personally test MineeMe. This article is based entirely on independent desk research: the product's official sales page (mineeme.com and products.olspsystem.com), GPT TOOLS 2 U product listings, a publicly available independent PDF review, third-party collection pages, JVZoo affiliate records, and social media promotional posts. Where a claim could not be independently verified — including all safety and reach claims — we say so explicitly.</p>
